sentences: In 1940–41 he co-founded a vocal quartet called Quartetto Egie, that changed line-up and name twice, becoming Quartetto Ritmo first and then Quartetto Cetra.
In 1964 Giacobetti married Valeria Fabrizi, an Italian actress, singer and television personality.
Giacobetti passed away in December 1998, a few months after Quartetto Cetra's final performance in Bologna.

sentences: Giovanni "Tata" Giacobetti (24 June 1922 – 2 December 1988) was an Italian singer and jazz musician.
